<B>Data type&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Description</B>
<BR>char(size)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
fixed-length character data, with a max size of 255
<BR>varchar2(size)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; variable-length character data, with
a max size of 2,000
<BR>varchar&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
currently the same as char
<BR>number(l,d)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; numeric data,
where "I" stands for length and "d" for the number of decimal digits
<BR>date&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
dates from January 1, 4712 B.C. to December 31, 4712 A.D.
<BR>long&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
variable-length character dta up to 2GB in size
