<P><FONT SIZE=+2>Select</FONT>

<P>The word <B>select </B>followed by what you want to see.&nbsp; This
is mandatory.
<BR>The word <B>from </B>followed by where you get it from.&nbsp; This
is mandatory.
<BR>The word <B>where </B>followed by any selection criteria.&nbsp; This
is optional.
<BR>The word <B>order by </B>followed by the sort criteria.&nbsp; This
is optional.

