<P><FONT SIZE=+2>Update, Delete and Alter</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2></FONT>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Update</FONT>

<P>The word <B>update </B>followed by the table you want to change.&nbsp;
This is mandatory.
<BR>The word <B>set </B>followed by one or more columns you want to change.&nbsp;
This si mandatory.
<BR>The word <B>where </B>followed by selection criteria.&nbsp; This is
optional.

<P><FONT SIZE=+2>(** example images **)</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2></FONT>
<br><IMG SRC="images/fig64.gif" width=600><br>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Delete</FONT>

<P>The words <B>delete from&nbsp;</B> followed by the table name you want
to remove data from.&nbsp; This is mandatory.
<BR>The word <B>where </B>followed by the criteria for the <B>delete</B>.&nbsp;
This is optional.

